&lt;p data-start=&quot;229&quot; data-end=&quot;453&quot;&gt;Are you passionate about helping designers elevate their creative workflows through advanced tooling? Do you enjoy empowering creative teams to adopt new technologies and drive meaningful impact in their day-to-day work?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;455&quot; data-end=&quot;923&quot;&gt;As the Creative Specialist at Smartly, you will enable designers to get the most value out of Smartly’s Creative Suite by delivering expert training, supporting strategic customer conversations, and ensuring seamless integration with industry-standard design tools. You will play a key role in driving product adoption, customer satisfaction, and long-term retention by equipping creative teams with the skills and knowledge to succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;930&quot; data-end=&quot;1014&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;934&quot; data-end=&quot;1014&quot;&gt;As the Creative Specialist at Smartly, you will…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1018&quot; data-end=&quot;1188&quot;&gt;Act as the main subject matter expert on Smartly’s Creative Suite and creative tooling, supporting Customer Success, Sales, and Product with advanced creative guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1191&quot; data-end=&quot;1344&quot;&gt;Partner closely with Customer Success to support pitches, demos, and exploratory creative conversations focused on advanced capabilities and workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1347&quot; data-end=&quot;1480&quot;&gt;Build and deliver training programs, workshops, and best practice sessions for new and experienced designers using Smartly’s tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1483&quot; data-end=&quot;1660&quot;&gt;Conduct expert-level live demos (virtual and in-person) to help designers integrate Smartly with Adobe Creative Cloud, Figma, After Effects, and other industry-standard tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1663&quot; data-end=&quot;1834&quot;&gt;Collaborate with teams across Customer Success, Sales, and Product to identify common creative pain points, upskilling needs, and opportunities to improve user adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1837&quot; data-end=&quot;1957&quot;&gt;Develop documentation, guides, tutorials, and templates to support ongoing creative education and self-serve learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1960&quot; data-end=&quot;2112&quot;&gt;Measure the effectiveness of training and enablement programs using adoption, retention, and customer feedback metrics, and iterate based on insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2115&quot; data-end=&quot;2284&quot;&gt;Stay current with design trends, creative software, AI in creative, and evolving advertising best practices to ensure Smartly’s creative training is modern and relevant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;2291&quot; data-end=&quot;2330&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2295&quot; data-end=&quot;2330&quot;&gt;We are looking for you, if you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2334&quot; data-end=&quot;2492&quot;&gt;Have at least 4 years of hands-on experience as a designer, with strong expertise in digital advertising, graphic design, UI/UX, illustration, or motion design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2495&quot; data-end=&quot;2623&quot;&gt;Are highly proficient in Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, Figma, After Effects, and familiar with HTML5 and other creative tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2626&quot; data-end=&quot;2714&quot;&gt;Have proven experience delivering creative or technical training to advanced learners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2717&quot; data-end=&quot;2803&quot;&gt;Can clearly communicate and demo complex creative concepts to experienced designers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2806&quot; data-end=&quot;2912&quot;&gt;Understand creative workflows end-to-end, especially within digital advertising and campaign production.&lt;

&lt;p&gt;Smartly.io is seeking an enthusiastic and detail-oriented Customer Onboarding Manager to join our dynamic Onboarding team. As a Customer Onboarding Manager, you will play a crucial role in assisting our newly-signed customers with the onboarding process, ensuring a seamless and successful transition to the Smartly platform. Your responsibilities will involve working closely with Sales and Customer Success teams to deliver optimal onboarding plans and solutions tailored to our key customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a subject matter expert on Smartly.io&#39;s products and services, understanding the platform&#39;s capabilities and effectively communicating and implementing solutions for potential and new customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Sales and Customer Success teams to deliver tailored solutions within the Smartly platform, enabling our Tier 1-3 key customers to achieve their business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of the technical execution of the onboarding plan, ensuring that customer accounts are set up for a successful and ongoing partnership with Smartly.io.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key Tasks:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Training clients on all key aspects of Smartly’s platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Showcase how to set up reporting views to provide customers with clear visibility into their campaign performance and key metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show how to use feeds to create automations and streamline customer workflows, optimizing efficiency and effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tailor the onboarding journey to each customer, understanding their specific challenges and finding solutions within the Smartly tool to drive product adoption and address any gaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of organizing and managing the onboarding process, relieving stressors from Customer Success Managers (CSMs) and collaborating with cross-functional teams at Smartly.io as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with relevant teams to qualify each case and ensure that all sales promises can be successfully delivered, fostering a culture where a deal is not considered closed until the customer is successfully onboarded.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create visually appealing and effective decks using Google Slides to communicate onboarding plans, campaign strategies, and performance insights to customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in a relevant field or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 - 5 years digital experience ideally ideally with exposure to both paid social (Meta) and programmatic media buying&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of digital advertising platforms and tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Google Sheets, utilizing its features and functions effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in creating visually appealing and impactful presentations using Google Slides.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to effectively engage with customers and internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detail-oriented and highly organized, with strong project management skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem-solving mindset and ability to navigate complex situations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated and proactive, with the ability to work independently and prioritize tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced and collaborative team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our team and contribute to the success of our clients as they embark on their Smartly.io journey. Help shape the onboarding experience and play a vital role in accelerating our customers&#39; time-to-value and long-term partnership.&lt;/p&gt;
