&lt;li&gt;Be the voice of customers to inform our sales process and product roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively across functions including Sales, Marketing, Technical Solutions, Services, Product and Engineering&lt;/li&gt;
