&lt;p&gt;This role focuses on owning and growing a portfolio of customers using Smartly’s social advertising platform. You will take full responsibility for your assigned clients, working independently to understand their business needs, create long-term value, and drive retention and growth. You sit at the intersection of customers, media partners, and internal teams to ensure strong outcomes across the customer lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you will do&lt;/h3&gt;
