&lt;li&gt;Worked in a start-up environment (a focus on Social or Ad-tech is a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multitask and prioritize and meet deadlines in a fast-moving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal, written and interpersonal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project Management skills and experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independent and well structured working style with can-do attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn fast learning and determination to achieve goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Google Workspace and Microsoft Office skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s Degree preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
